Comment: 0,0:07:10.30,0:07:11.40,Alt,,0,0,0,,Woah.
Comment: 0,0:08:13.10,0:08:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Comment: 0,0:08:14.10,0:08:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A god but you say "Elhit"?
Comment: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Arrgh!
Comment: 0,0:08:02.65,0:08:04.30,orig,,0,0,0,,I couldn't care less.
Comment: 0,0:04:29.15,0:04:30.45,orig,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Comment: 0,0:04:33.65,0:04:36.15,orig,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Comment: 0,0:05:17.30,0:05:17.95,orig,,0,0,0,,Woah!
Comment: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:16.85,orig,,0,0,0,,Woohoo! Yeah, got my third Vice!
Comment: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:46.80,orig,,0,0,0,,It doesn't really matter.
Comment: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:58.35,orig,,0,0,0,,You can't {\i1}own {\i0}a daemon{demon}.
Comment: 0,0:08:04.30,0:08:05.15,orig,,0,0,0,,Same here.
Comment: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:54.55,orig,,0,0,0,,My Dear White God Elhit is a huge wolf, and has a big heart, so I don't think Dear Elhit would get mad because of that.
Comment: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:52.45,orig,,0,0,0,,What the heck!
Comment: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:49.85,orig,,0,0,0,,O-Oh... You don't say.
Comment: 0,0:10:49.85,0:10:52.00,orig,,0,0,0,,Now that really doesn't fit you.
Comment: 0,0:12:05.75,0:12:06.60,orig,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's go.
Comment: 0,0:13:13.40,0:13:14.30,orig,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Comment: 0,0:14:54.50,0:14:55.20,orig,,0,0,0,,You can't...?
Comment: 0,0:14:55.75,0:14:57.16,orig,,0,0,0,,You can't use your magic?
Comment: 0,0:15:04.10,0:15:05.80,orig,,0,0,0,,Manato, tell us!
Comment: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:21.30,orig,,0,0,0,,What? Why are you apologizing? What, Manato? What?!
Comment: 0,0:15:25.35,0:15:26.50,orig,,0,0,0,,Counting... on you...
Comment: 0,0:15:27.10,0:15:29.05,orig,,0,0,0,,Counting on me to what?
Comment: 0,0:15:35.75,0:15:37.10,orig,,0,0,0,,Manato! No way.
Comment: 0,0:15:43.20,0:15:44.15,orig,,0,0,0,,The arrow, we need to pull it out.
Comment: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:05.00,orig,,0,0,0,,I beg of you!
Comment: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:08.80,orig,,0,0,0,,I'll do anything, so please!
Comment: 0,0:16:09.45,0:16:13.97,orig,,0,0,0,,Please, save him! Please. I beg you!
Comment: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:28.60,orig,,0,0,0,,Why?
Comment: 0,0:16:47.25,0:16:49.80,orig,,0,0,0,,This must be a mistake.
Comment: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:07.52,orig,,0,0,0,,Manato said that it was scary and dangerous,
Comment: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:11.00,orig,,0,0,0,,and together we thought about how we could do better.
Comment: 0,0:17:12.00,0:17:14.95,orig,,0,0,0,,And that if we can overcome this, we can keep moving forward.
Comment: 0,0:17:26.10,0:17:35.00,orig,,0,0,0,,Those who are not buried properly in these borderlands\Nturn into No Life King's servants because of his curse.
Comment: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:37.65,orig,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the heck?!
Comment: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:14.25,orig,,0,0,0,,That means... we have to c-cremate Manato?
Comment: 0,0:18:15.80,0:18:16.75,orig,,0,0,0,,That is correct.
Comment: 0,0:18:32.75,0:18:35.80,orig,,0,0,0,,And I assume that costs money, too?
Comment: 0,0:18:49.05,0:18:49.75,orig,,0,0,0,,No, thank you.

Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.85,0:00:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, could you wait a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.80,0:01:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to try, Shihoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.25,0:01:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.40,0:01:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I-I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.25,0:01:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, they won't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.35,0:01:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.70,0:01:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.95,0:02:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.65,0:02:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.25,0:02:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally got to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You want some, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.95,0:02:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You like animals?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.65,0:02:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.70,0:02:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.45,0:02:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.15,0:02:49.55,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Repeating a yesterday filled with scrapes,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.55,0:02:54.35,op/ed,,0,0,0,,We clear the path to a hopeful tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:09.45,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I wonder what remains
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.45,0:03:12.65,op/ed,,0,0,0,,in both these tiny hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:19.00,op/ed,,0,0,0,,The voice I raised upwards scattered into the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:22.30,op/ed,,0,0,0,,The reality I've gamed is hazy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:25.40,op/ed,,0,0,0,,and even if I can't see ahead of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.40,0:03:28.70,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I can keep moving forward on this long road
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:32.80,op/ed,,0,0,0,,if I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.80,0:03:39.05,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Connecting a bond covered in dust,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.05,0:03:45.40,op/ed,,0,0,0,,We join back to back in the past and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:51.85,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Repeating an answer full of mistakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.85,0:03:59.85,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I will reach out my hands to seek the light, again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.25,0:04:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Go all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that even mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.15,0:04:30.45,fix,,0,0,0,,Who knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I've heard it before, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.65,0:04:36.15,fix,,0,0,0,,I feel like that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.65,0:04:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranta! One's heading your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.85,0:04:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, you don't have to tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:48.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,That's Ranta's new skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.30,0:04:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh— You're no ordinary goblin, are you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obviously just an ordinary goblin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:02.80,Italics,,0,0,0,,Ranta wasn't the only one who learned a new skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.50,0:05:07.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,We all learned a new skill from our respective guilds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:12.05,Italics,,0,0,0,,But since they're new skills, we don't have\Nthe confidence to use them in a real fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:17.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,But if we don't try them,\Nwe'll never be able to make use of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:25.15,Italics,,0,0,0,,Yume's new skill, Diagonal Cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:29.35,Italics,,0,0,0,,Yume chose to learn a skill for a\Nshort-range weapon rather than for a bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.45,0:05:27.30,Alt,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.95,0:05:30.75,Italics,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.30,0:05:35.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,Back Stab.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.75,0:05:41.05,Italics,,0,0,0,,Wait, did I hit a vital spot?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:41.05,Alt,,0,0,0,,I'll deal the final blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:42.60,Italics,,0,0,0,,Maybe I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:43.25,Alt,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,0:05:44.35,Alt,,0,0,0,,I got another Vice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.95,0:05:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark Knights are such savages.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that every battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a savage!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Say "atrocious," it's more elegant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.30,0:05:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We atrocious Dark Knights serve the Dark God, Skullhell-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We're cold and ruthless knights having neither blood nor tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.45,0:06:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohm, Rel, Ect, Well, Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:09.50,Italics,,0,0,0,,Shadow Beat Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:14.30,Italics,,0,0,0,,Mages can use the power from\Nmagical beings called "elementals."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:19.40,Italics,,0,0,0,,Shihoru decided to learn how to use shadow elementals.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Smash.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.50,0:06:32.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,Those in the Priest Guild can't use weapons with a blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:40.50,Italics,,0,0,0,,In our party, Manato is both healer and vanguard,\Nso this is a critical skill for him to have.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatred!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.45,0:06:48.95,Italics,,0,0,0,,Good, they've locked blades.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:51.35,Italics,,0,0,0,,Moguzo has the advantage now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:55.60,Italics,,0,0,0,,This is Moguzo's new skill, Wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:06:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Moguzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:07:00.45,Alt,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:02.35,Italics,,0,0,0,,Rage Blow, or the Thanks Slash.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.25,0:07:07.25,Italics,,0,0,0,,For some reason, he always says "thanks!" so we call it that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.25,0:07:11.25,Italics,,0,0,0,,Like the name suggests, its strength is nothing to underestimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:13.00,fix,,0,0,0,,Woohoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.00,0:07:14.35,fix,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:16.85,fix,,0,0,0,,With this I get my third Vice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This will power up my daemon{demon}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.05,0:07:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it'll whisper to enemies and lower their defenses!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Only if it feels like it, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark Knight daemons{demons} are so useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I can't let that slide, Haruhiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.50,0:07:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop dissing my buddy, Zodiaco!{ゾヂィアックん; ゾヂィアック = Zodiac [see jp.wiki for "Zodiac Killer"), then he just added N at the end in hiragana, so it sounds and reads as Zodiac-kun, or rather Zodiakun, but should be Zodiac[ending syllable]. So it's either Zodiaca, Zodiace, Zodiaco, or Zodiacu.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:39.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,Ranta named his daemon{demon} "Zodiaco."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.75,0:07:44.45,Italics,,0,0,0,,No, I think his proper name is "Zodiac"\Nand his nickname is "Zodiaco."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:46.85,Italics,,0,0,0,,In any case it doesn't really matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Zodiaco is kinda cute, which is\Nthe complete opposite of his owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.55,0:07:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not his owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:58.65,fix,,0,0,0,,You can't {\i1}own {\i0}a daemon{demon}, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.65,0:08:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more like Zodiaco's possessing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.65,0:08:04.35,fix,,0,0,0,,I couldn't care less in any case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:05.35,fix,,0,0,0,,Truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Manato?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.90,0:08:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I need to pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{My Dear }White God Elhit-chan, thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's some of my food...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.55,0:08:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...so please keep watching over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a Hunter Guild practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Elhit-chan protects Hunters, so we\Ncan be safe while hunting and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, you call him with "chan"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.65,0:08:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:48.55,fix,,0,0,0,,{My Dear }White God Elhit-chan, you know, is a very huge wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:54.60,fix,,0,0,0,,And he has a big heart, so I don't think\N{Dear Elhit} he would get mad because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually haven't gotten scolded before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:09:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I think your God understands your feelings, Yume.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.20,0:09:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think that feelings are really important.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.45,0:09:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I have lots and lots of feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,At night we all go to sleep, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.90,0:09:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I'm sleeping, I dream about {Dear }Elhit-chan a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.80,0:09:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I ask Elhit-chan, "Can I ride on your back?"\Nand {Dear }Elhit-chan takes off and runs, super fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.35,0:09:36.50,Alt,,0,0,0,,And I'm like, "Woah, this is so cool!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There better be a point to this story.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been patiently listening to you until now,\Nso I'll whack you if there isn't a really good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A point?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:52.50,fix,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go rambling on if there's no point to what you're saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking what a good party we've become.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.15,0:10:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We can now usually defeat three goblins at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If we change our strategy, maybe we can do four.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Moguzo is our reliable shield, like a defensive tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.60,0:10:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He's big, strong, and overpowers our enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,His sword strikes accurately, and he\Nmakes good attacks when needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.50,0:10:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree, Moguzo's really good with his hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.90,0:10:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.95,0:10:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why, but I like doing detailed work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.25,0:10:34.95,Alt,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't fit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.75,0:10:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're amazing too, Ranta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.75,0:10:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially how you're always ready to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest of us are more on the careful side.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.50,0:10:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If you weren't here, there would have been times\Nwhen we wouldn't have been able to advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:48.40,fix,,0,0,0,,O-Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.40,0:10:49.85,fix,,0,0,0,,W-Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.85,0:10:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't fit you too, Ranta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And Yume, you're never afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:11:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of all of us, you're probably the bravest one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to be cautious as the healer, but if anything were\Nto happen, I know that you'll always be there to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The bravest?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess there aren't many things I'm afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.55,0:11:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you'll be patient with\Na Hunter who's not great with a bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody has things they aren't good at or can't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.55,0:11:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We cover each other's weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what a party's for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And Shihoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.15,0:11:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Shihoru is always aware of her surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Shadow magic mostly has spells\Nto confuse and bind enemies, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,These can be used to help friends if need be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You learned shadow magic because\Nyou want to be able to help, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been here for a while, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start our afternoon work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.75,0:12:10.65,Italics,,0,0,0,,What about me, Manato?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.55,0:12:13.75,Italics,,0,0,0,,Oh well, I can ask him anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:16.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,There are many other chances to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.15,0:12:21.40,Italics,,0,0,0,,Or... so I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruhiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,0:12:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruhiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:48.15,Alt,,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.15,0:12:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Haru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.75,0:12:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It really hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.90,0:12:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:52.80,Alt,,0,0,0,,Ow ow ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.60,0:13:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,O Light, return to Lumiares' divine protection. Cure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.40,0:13:14.30,fix,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.20,0:13:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shihoru, fall back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.85,0:13:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Moguzo, another one's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.85,0:13:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Retreat for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.10,0:13:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Haruhiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Your idea to map out this place... came in handy, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Manato?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.80,0:14:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Manato?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Manato?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Manato!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, hurry and use your magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:55.20,fix,,0,0,0,,Magic is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:56.95,fix,,0,0,0,,You can't use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:14:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I-If you meditate for a while—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:05.00,fix,,0,0,0,,Manato...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:06.10,fix,,0,0,0,,Tell us, Manato!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.65,0:15:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us, Manato!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.95,0:15:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Manato!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Haru...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...hiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sor... ry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.40,0:15:19.45,fix,,0,0,0,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.05,0:15:21.45,fix,,0,0,0,,What, Manato? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:26.50,fix,,0,0,0,,Entrust you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.10,0:15:27.95,fix,,0,0,0,,Entrust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.95,0:15:29.35,fix,,0,0,0,,Entrust me what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.35,0:15:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Manato!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.55,0:15:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to tell me or I won't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.40,0:15:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Manato.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.75,0:15:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Manato!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Manato!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.75,0:15:37.10,fix,,0,0,0,,Manato, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Manato!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We have to stop the blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.45,0:15:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And do mouth-to-mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.90,0:15:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Lay him down! Gently!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.20,0:15:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull out the arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready? I'm taking it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Gently!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready, pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:03.50,fix,,0,0,0,,I beg of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:05.10,fix,,0,0,0,,I beg of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.55,0:16:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Please save Manato!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:08.85,fix,,0,0,0,,I'll do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:10.15,fix,,0,0,0,,So please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:11.50,fix,,0,0,0,,I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.95,0:16:13.60,fix,,0,0,0,,Please. Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:28.75,fix,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can bring the dead back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.50,0:16:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Manato, how could you be so foolish?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.05,0:16:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A youth who showed such promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.25,0:16:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Alas, your life has fallen away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard, don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.30,0:16:50.05,fix,,0,0,0,,This... must be some a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we let our guard down a little back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.40,0:16:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.15,0:16:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But, we managed to scrape by today, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.55,0:17:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruhiro...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And Manato...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:07.40,fix,,0,0,0,,M-Manato s-said that it was scary and d-dangerous...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.05,0:17:11.10,fix,,0,0,0,,...and t-together we t-thought about\Nhow we could do better... and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.95,0:17:14.50,fix,,0,0,0,,...if we can overcome this, we can keep moving forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.10,0:17:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we can... continue again... tomorrow—!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You must give him a proper funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:35.35,fix,,0,0,0,,Because of the curse of No Life King, those who are not\Nburied properly in these borderlands turn into his servants.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:38.05,fix,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the heck is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You have five days at most.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.55,0:17:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There have been instances when\Nthey become moving corpses at three.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.30,0:17:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sure nobody wishes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...to see a comrade in that state.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.95,0:18:07.15,fix,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:14.35,fix,,0,0,0,,That means... we have to... c-cremate... Manato?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.80,0:18:16.80,fix,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.70,0:18:33.90,fix,,0,0,0,,And that too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:35.80,fix,,0,0,0,,...costs money, I presume.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't have the funds, I will pay it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.85,0:18:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.05,0:18:49.90,fix,,0,0,0,,No need.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.75,0:18:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Manato is my...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...is our...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...is our...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...friend.
